OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774786269
OL,3,CFamily of terminally ill man beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath by UDA recieves death threats
OL,6,FAn 82-year-old woman whose terminally
OL,7,Fill son was murdered has been warned
OL,8,Fby police that there is a threat
OL,9,Fagainst her life.
OL,11,FIt is the fourth threat Ellen Quinn
OL,12,Fhas received after her son, Glenn was
OL,13,Fbeaten by members of the South East
OL,14,FAntrim UDA in January 2020.
OL,16,FThe 47-year-old was found dead in his
OL,17,Fground floor flat at Ashleigh Park in
OL,18,Fthe Woodburn area of Carrickfergus.
OL,20,FNo one has ever been convicted of his
OL,21,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
