OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774786269
OL,3,CFamily of terminally ill man beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath by UDA recieves death threats
OL,6,FMs Quinn's other son Martin has also
OL,7,Fbeen told he is in imminent danger.
OL,9,FThe PSNI said they are continuing to
OL,10,F"engage with the family of Glenn Quinn
OL,11,Faround any concerns they may have".
OL,13,FSpeaking to UTV, Ellen said: "They
OL,14,Fcouldn't hurt me any more than what
OL,15,Fthey've already done. They took my son
OL,16,Faway from me. I will never see him
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,19,F"I didn't put my arms around him and
OL,20,Fhold him. They took my son."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774786269
OL,3,CFamily of terminally ill man beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath by UDA recieves death threats
OL,6,FMs Quinn had just returned home from
OL,7,Fshopping when her son Martin rang to
OL,8,Ftell her two police officers were
OL,9,Fgoing to visit.
OL,11,FThe officers told her they had
OL,12,Fintelligence that members of an
OL,13,Forganised crime gang intend to carry
OL,14,Fout a violent attack and the use of a
OL,15,Fgun couldn't be ruled out.
OL,17,FMartin Quinn told UTV: "Mum is the
OL,18,Fstrongest of us all, we get all our
OL,19,Fstrength from my mum and they're
OL,20,Ftrying to silence her by threatening
OL,21,Fto shoot an 82-year-old woman.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774786269
OL,3,CFamily of terminally ill man beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath by UDA recieves death threats
OL,6,F"It's a disgrace. They're absolutely
OL,7,Fdespicable."
OL,9,F"I have to be concerned. I have to be
OL,10,Fworried because Glenn received a
OL,11,Fsimilar threat and four days later,
OL,12,FGlenn was murdered."
OL,14,FDUP Leader Gavin Robinson MP said: "I
OL,15,Fthink it's utterly appalling. A family
OL,16,Fquesting for justice, wanting to see
OL,17,Fjustice for the loss of their loved
OL,18,Fone, their brother and their son.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
