PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774786269
OL,3,CFamily of terminally ill man beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath by UDA recieves death threats
OL,6,F"Cowards who skulk in the night and
OL,7,Fthreaten 82-year-old mothers, it needs
OL,8,Fto be condemned."
OL,10,FPSNI Mid & East Antrim District
OL,11,FCommander, Superintendent William
OL,12,FCalderwood, said: "The confidence of
OL,13,Fthe communities we serve is always at
OL,14,Fthe forefront of our minds and keeping
OL,15,Fpeople safe will always be our
OL,16,Fpriority.
OL,26,@tD@SOU
