PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774786269
OL,3,CFamily of terminally ill man beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath by UDA recieves death threats
OL,6,F"I want to reassure the public that
OL,7,Fofficers and staff are working around
OL,8,Fthe clock to prevent crime and harm to
OL,9,Findividuals, protect the vulnerable
OL,10,Fand detect those who commit crime and
OL,11,Fbring them before the courts.
OL,13,F"Should any member of the public have
OL,14,Fconcern about criminality in their
OL,15,Flocal area, we would ask them to
OL,16,Fplease share it with police by calling
OL,17,Fus on 101, we will always take
OL,18,Fappropriate steps to address the issue
OL,19,Fand safeguard our communities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
