OL,3,CFamily of terminally ill man beaten to
OL,4,Cdeath by UDA recieves death threats
OL,6,F"We continue to engage with the family
OL,7,Fof Glenn Quinn around any concerns
OL,8,Fthey may have.
OL,10,F"We understand their suffering
OL,11,Ffollowing his senseless loss and our
OL,12,Fappeal for any information which may
OL,13,Fprovide the answers or justice they
OL,14,Fdeserve is ongoing."
